gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 126, Spurs 119
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Luka Doncic's 33 points, 14 rebounds and 10 assists, the Mavericks defeated the Spurs,126-119.  Kyrie Irving added 22 points (10 in the 4th quarter) and 6 assists in the victory.  Devin Vassell tallied 23 points, 5 rebounds and 3 assists for the Spurs, while Victor Wembanyama added 15 points, 5 rebounds, 2 assists, 2 steals and 3 3pt. FG in his debut in the losing effort. The Mavericks improve to 1-0 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 0-1.
